{"tid":369491,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是日晚餐 蒸三文魚皮","createTime":"2017-08-22T11:12:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-24T13:02:01.000Z","uid":123204,"like":26,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fde0b86ce956ab0190d28015506ea58481b848ac","tid":369491,"uid":123204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T11:12:10.000Z","msg":"話說香港人真係好鍾意食三文魚<br />\n成日話有蟲 但食放題又會一盤盤三文魚咁上<br />\n食壽司基本上又係主打三文魚<br />\n<br />\n閒時都會去壽司鋪買包三文魚皮❨17蚊❩返去蒸 <br />\n壽司鋪師傅廣東話同英文都係麻麻哋<br />\n但日文又幾流利<br />\n見佢扮得咁有心 應該啲料都ok<br />\n不過一包六條要食足三晚先清曬會悶先先<br />\n<br />\n如果咩野都唔落基本上麻煩度都係3-4分左右 ❨10分滿分❩<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/4iuwcn01\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F4iuwcn01&h=3c1014d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n側側頭唔好意思<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n材料 3-4人份<br />\n三文魚皮2條<br />\n少量鹽<br />\n<br />\n調味試過用蒜蓉 黑椒 同欖角<br />\n有次招呼個韓妹食就勁鍾意食欖角 當堂成包比佢拎走<br />\n不過今日簡單啲落鹽算"},{"pid":"cb5ebd56e4e70ec1c5d77507975134d58eab36ee","tid":369491,"uid":1096,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T11:21:13.000Z","msg":"食韓妹 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91e36cb7ab49de272de473447b7440fbaeec1b3c","tid":369491,"uid":123204,"like":2,"dislike":22,"score":-20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T11:24:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/7w4ecgju\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F7w4ecgju&h=2a38ab51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n安全起見都係洗下先<br />\n希望洗走啲蟲蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6810de0991a38a9b4bd211000a02f725c15bc42f","tid":369491,"uid":59356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T11:26:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a048f4d8aad76d948f9e9fa730e18f206e096680","tid":369491,"uid":29485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T11:26:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fce062ff8b01894e24f423c7825ef376bdbbe1fb","tid":369491,"uid":138510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T11:26:59.000Z","msg":"98"},{"pid":"e45e2e336d4e6901a2aade3b9b4f284deed55ead","tid":369491,"uid":2076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T11:29:33.000Z","msg":"炸試過未？"},{"pid":"1a2a10af0018a91e6e6fae2c2180283cd3220505","tid":369491,"uid":123204,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T11:29:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/sme31ird\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fsme31ird&h=bc300a3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n洗好都係簡單切一塊塊<br />\n為免洗多樣就針板都唔用凌空切<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/6e0g27rz\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F6e0g27rz&h=56fb55d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n落啲玫瑰鹽<br />\n<br />\n同場整埋個水蛋就入爐"},{"pid":"8388c888e752e21522ddfe6eda8d3430df59278d","tid":369491,"uid":123204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T11:30:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>炸試過未？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上生粉空氣炸<br />\n不過功夫多 好耐無整"},{"pid":"06bcc3ce5978196a39e4f4ee11534c8f40bc24b5","tid":369491,"uid":56878,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T11:31:27.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"0368fc1720239de5ea19e3c8a4d0e5ce76422d09","tid":369491,"uid":30377,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T11:33:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>炸試過未？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上生粉空氣炸<br />\n不過功夫多 好耐無整</blockquote><br />\n但蒸食落口感會唔會好核突？<br />\n我好唔鐘意食魚皮 但炸魚皮就鐘意"},{"pid":"2c6f98713850feb98eb9caecd045aa5381300a7e","tid":369491,"uid":123204,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T11:36:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>炸試過未？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上生粉空氣炸<br />\n不過功夫多 好耐無整</blockquote><br />\n但蒸食落口感會唔會好核突？<br />\n我好唔鐘意食魚皮 但炸魚皮就鐘意</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔會架<br />\n唔同炸魚皮咁淨得皮 <br />\n好係皮邊肉咁<br />\n食落同火炙三文魚差唔多"},{"pid":"2b7716a633168e26a443b1fe1351a2128019a98f","tid":369491,"uid":138799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T11:39:50.000Z","msg":"唔食生野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"994d722a6ce4d6245f1cefc30051186316367979","tid":369491,"uid":123204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T11:41:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔食生野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屋企人都係咁上下 唔鍾意刺身<br />\n整黎個就fit 到佢地 ❨仲平好多❩"},{"pid":"a6471b454c2387bd4d3fd78066291c61b26f0742","tid":369491,"uid":129829,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T11:43:22.000Z","msg":"魚皮好核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff389dd2469c6ed0deb5448b72fcc124ccd099e5","tid":369491,"uid":138799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T11:47:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔食生野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屋企人都係咁上下 唔鍾意刺身<br />\n整黎個就fit 到佢地 ❨仲平好多❩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n整個白汁三文魚蜆肉意粉啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d8de2b93d666f03f0696d3e730ca140f86ab3d5","tid":369491,"uid":123204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T11:48:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔食生野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屋企人都係咁上下 唔鍾意刺身<br />\n整黎個就fit 到佢地 ❨仲平好多❩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n整個白汁三文魚蜆肉意粉啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" cla